ENAITURUK

Ore empalai e YOHANA e dukuya neeta imbaa are sapuki: (
1  ) Pee eitagol ilaisumak metotoni te nchula o Enkai o Enkerai enye, Yesu Kristo (
2  ) neikok ninche tenkaraki esujata oo nkiteng'enat e lejare naaidim aainyiala ina shula e Nkai.

Ore apa ena kiteng'enare, netiu anaa keitamoki apa iltung'ana aajoki ore eng'oki neewuo enkaraki naibung'are oltung'ani ena kop, neaku ore Yesu, ina Kerai e Nkai nemeidimayu apa pee eaku oltung'ani. Etejo apa lelo aiteng'enak inchere pooki ake pee eaku oltung'ani olotajeuo tukul naa tinikilakuni katukul too mbaa ena kishon e nkop. Etejo sii nchere ore enjeunoto nemeeta eneporoki mbaa naaipirta eloloito arashu enyorrata te likae tung'ani liboitare.

Ore eanyata eina kiteng'enare, eibalie olasirani aitawang katukul ajo ore apa Yesu Kristo, netaa ninye oltung'ani, neitadedeyie oleng ajo ore pooki ooiruk Yesu nenyor Enkai, neishiaakino pee enyorruno sii ninche maate.

